---
/* AboutUs.astro */
---

<section id="about" class="section section-concrete">
  <div class="container about-container">
    <!-- Left Column: Visual Collage -->
    <div class="about-visual reveal">
      <div class="about-image-wrapper">
        <img 
          src="/barista.png" 
          alt="Proses Pembuatan Kopi Spesialti di Bura Bura Coffee" 
          class="about-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <!-- Accent Frame overlay -->
        <div class="accent-frame"></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Mini floating stat card -->
      <div class="floating-stat-card glass-card">
        <span class="stat-icon">☕</span>
        <div class="stat-text">
          <span class="stat-value">Sugar-Less</span>
          <span class="stat-desc">Enjoyable & Accessible</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Story Text -->
    <div class="about-content reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <span class="badge">Tentang Kami</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Menolak Manis Buatan, <br/>
        <span class="text-gradient-blue">Merayakan Cita Rasa Murni</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="story-paragraph highlight">
        "To redefine coffee culture by making sugar-less coffee enjoyable, accessible, and loved by everyone."
      </p>
      <p class="story-paragraph">
        Di Bura Bura Coffee, kami percaya bahwa setiap biji kopi memiliki cerita rasa tersendiri—aroma buah yang segar, rasa manis madu alami, hingga sentuhan cokelat yang pekat. Menambahkan gula berlebih sering kali menutupi keindahan rasa asli ini. 
      </p>
      <p class="story-paragraph">
        Itulah mengapa kami memelopori budaya kopi tanpa gula tambahan. Melalui teknik sangrai yang presisi dan ekstraksi ristretto yang dikalibrasi ketat, kami membuktikan bahwa kopi murni bisa dinikmati oleh semua orang dengan rasa yang bulat, lembut, dan tanpa rasa pahit yang mengganggu.
      </p>
      
      <div class="philosophy-grid">
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="phil-icon-wrapper">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="phil-details">
            <h3 class="phil-title">Pilihan Lebih Sehat</h3>
            <p class="phil-desc">Nikmati kafein harian Anda tanpa khawatir akan kalori kosong dan lonjakan gula darah.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="phil-icon-wrapper">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9.09 9 1-1a3 3 0 0 1 5.91 1 3 3 0 0 1-2.91 3h-.09M12 17h.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="phil-details">
            <h3 class="phil-title">Ristretto Base</h3>
            <p class="phil-desc">Menggunakan potongan ekstraksi ristretto yang lebih manis dan pekat sebagai bahan dasar minuman kami.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Visual Column */
  .about-visual {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .about-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 2;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .about-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .about-image-wrapper:hover .about-image {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .accent-frame {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: -20px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-blue-primary);
    border-radius: 20px;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .about-visual:hover .accent-frame {
    transform: translate(8px, -8px);
    border-color: var(--color-blue-light);
  }

  /* Floating Stat Card */
  .floating-stat-card {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 30px;
    right: -20px;
    z-index: 3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 240px;
  }

  .stat-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .stat-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light-muted);
  }

  /* Content Column */
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .story-paragraph {
    color: var(--color-text-light-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-paragraph.highlight {
    font-family: var(--font-subheading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-blue-light);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-blue-primary);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Philosophy Items */
  .philosophy-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .philosophy-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .phil-icon-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: var(--color-blue-glow);
    color: var(--color-blue-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .phil-title {
    font-family: var(--font-subheading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .phil-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Responsive Adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    .about-visual {
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .accent-frame {
      left: 20px;
    }

    .floating-stat-card {
      right: 10%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .floating-stat-card {
      display: none;
    }
    
    .about-image-wrapper {
      max-width: 320px;
    }
    
    .accent-frame {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
